{
  "stem": "17001.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then another girl would say, oh, I know a very good recipe the way my mother used to make it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then another one say, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is the way to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our mouth is dripping, and our mouth is watering to-- to have all that smell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not-- not-- not the food, just the smell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the meantime, us we are seated there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We see that the lice were so big that they were leaving a track as they were passing by.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one morning, I walked-- I went out before the [GERMAN], and I went near the ambulatory where they were collecting or experimenting with people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had seen this woman front of the-- side of the-- the-- the ambulatory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And her feet is standing like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And gray.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The whole body gray.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they wrapped in a blanket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I look at the side of the windows, and I see in the windows-- which none of the barrack had windows, but that one had-- there was a glass that had like a little slimy things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was another one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It looked a little bigger, like a little minnow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then another glass, there was a little more like a ball sort of slimy thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the other glass, there was like-- you see that small little thing like a-- like a turtle, like a frog, is all bundled up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the other one, and until finally there was a shape of a baby.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you were able to see the little nails on the-- on the baby, and it curled up like-- like a ball.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then you see in the next glass there was a regular baby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But like-- like a little doll, like a miniature one.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
